## Batik Filter Search [/batik/harga/{keyword}/{min}/{max}]

Search batiks from Batikita's database using a keyword and a price range. It will retrieve all batiks from database that match the keyword and the price range. This action returns a 200 status code along with a JSON body.

+ Parameters
    + keyword (String) - keyword to search for batik
    + min (Integer) - min price for batik with selected keyword
    + max (Integer) - max price for batik with selected keyword

